attributes.description: Overview dashboard for RabbitMQ managed by AmazonMQ.

params.markdown:
## RabbitMQ

This dashboard provides insights into RabbitMQ in AmazonMQ, covering:

- Broker resource utilization, including CPU, memory, and storage.
- Connection metrics, including the number of broker connections, producers, consumers, message count, and processing rates.
- Topic-level metrics such as enqueue/dequeue counts, enqueue time, and the number of producers / consumers.
- Queue-level metrics, including enqueue/dequeue counts, enqueue time, and the number of producers / consumers.
